🎬 IMDB Movie Review Sentiment Analysis (Simple RNN)
📌 Project Overview

This project is a Sentiment Analysis Web App built using a Simple Recurrent Neural Network (RNN) trained on the IMDB movie review dataset.

The model classifies movie reviews as:

✅ Positive

❌ Negative

The application is deployed using Streamlit, allowing users to enter custom movie reviews and get instant predictions.

🚀 Demo

Enter a movie review in the text box and click "Classify" to see:

Predicted Sentiment

Confidence Score

🧠 Model Architecture

Embedding Layer

Simple RNN Layer

Dense Output Layer (Sigmoid activation)

The model was trained on the IMDB dataset available in TensorFlow/Keras.

